darwin/libproc	Apple macOS / Darwin
freebsd	FreeBSD
n+obsd	NetBSD / OpenBSD
n+os	NEXTSTEP / OpenStep
sun	Solaris / SunOS
aix	IBM AIX
du	DEC/Compaq/HP Tru64 UNIX
